WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.100
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.100 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 2]

01:24.670 --> 01:25.340
Who's there?

01:47.240 --> 01:48.170
It's you...

01:48.940 --> 01:50.010
It's you!

01:50.600 --> 01:51.580
You followed me again!

01:52.800 --> 01:54.220
Followed you?

01:56.830 --> 01:58.730
I have no money for an inn, so I can only stay here.

01:59.520 --> 02:01.940
I was here first anyway.

02:03.240 --> 02:05.940
When did you get here? What did you hear?

02:06.720 --> 02:07.650
I slept

02:09.270 --> 02:12.060
until the aroma of roast chicken woke me.

02:23.900 --> 02:24.650
Sir,

02:26.110 --> 02:27.900
have we met somewhere before?

02:32.390 --> 02:34.900
I'm Lei Xiuyuan, an exam applicant.

02:35.960 --> 02:38.180
I think we've never met.

02:40.620 --> 02:41.940
We're here for the exam too.

02:42.870 --> 02:45.250
Fate brought us together. Let's journey together

02:45.480 --> 02:46.940
and look out for each other.

02:47.590 --> 02:48.410
- Great idea... - No way!

02:53.320 --> 02:55.090
Who are you? What's your motive?

02:55.800 --> 02:56.570
Speak properly, Xiaobangchui.

02:56.590 --> 02:57.250
Quiet!

02:57.760 --> 03:00.300
First your brother, then the academy exam.

03:00.710 --> 03:02.220
As if I'd believe you. Speak!

03:08.710 --> 03:12.220
Chufeng Academy is the safest place in the world.

03:13.150 --> 03:15.970
It remains neutral through immortal feuds

03:16.320 --> 03:17.370
and mortal wars alike.

03:18.990 --> 03:19.940
My brother is in danger.

03:21.670 --> 03:24.850
Only by getting into the academy can I save him.

03:31.390 --> 03:33.180
You said your master's lost.

03:33.390 --> 03:34.850
Why take the academy exam suddenly?

03:35.800 --> 03:36.370
I…?

03:36.870 --> 03:38.650
I need to improve my skills to find my master.

03:39.830 --> 03:40.530
Me too.

03:41.360 --> 03:42.220
Only strength

03:42.760 --> 03:43.900
can protect the ones I love.

04:13.520 --> 04:14.370
Why keep staring at me?

04:15.990 --> 04:17.090
I'm not that tomboy.

04:24.880 --> 04:26.370
Xigu Village lies in Gaolu.

04:26.790 --> 04:27.890
Since you're from Gaolu,

04:28.560 --> 04:29.770
do you know Mr. Lei, the military commander?

04:40.880 --> 04:41.810
Gaolu is long gone.

04:42.390 --> 04:45.250
I have no country, no home left.

04:45.790 --> 04:46.770
No country, no home…

04:47.790 --> 04:48.570
I'm just like you,

04:49.590 --> 04:51.100
homeless and stateless.

04:55.710 --> 04:58.060
Your clothes are torn. My sister can sew.

04:58.470 --> 04:59.740
Let her mend them for you.

05:01.100 --> 05:01.810
No need.

05:02.700 --> 05:04.540
We have trials tomorrow. Better look decent.

05:18.900 --> 05:19.740
Your Highness.

05:19.780 --> 05:20.090
[Young Ye Ye]

05:20.090 --> 05:21.300
Hurry, take off your robe and give it to him.

05:21.830 --> 05:24.100
Yuan, Mr. Lei died defending our realm.

05:24.390 --> 05:25.420
As his adopted son,

05:25.700 --> 05:28.210
you must safeguard His Highness like him.

05:28.710 --> 05:29.500
Do you understand?

05:41.660 --> 05:42.890
Are you truly unfamiliar with Mr. Lei?

05:43.230 --> 05:45.890
I'll say this one last time: I do not know him.

05:46.340 --> 05:47.420
Forget the torn clothes.

05:47.460 --> 05:48.500
Hurry undress and get some sleep.

05:48.540 --> 05:49.660
Don't you remember why we came to Lugong Town?

05:59.710 --> 06:00.450
My apologies.

06:01.540 --> 06:02.770
I must've missed my old friend so much

06:03.460 --> 06:04.210
that I mistook you for him.

06:15.460 --> 06:16.890
[Lugong Town]
The spirit root test begins.

06:51.560 --> 06:54.210
Fire Spirit Root. Pass.

07:00.120 --> 07:01.420
You're amazing!

07:01.560 --> 07:02.500
You'll definitely rank first.

07:04.470 --> 07:06.180
What's a single Fire Spirit Root?

07:06.640 --> 07:09.940
Spirit roots correspond to the Five Elements: Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, Earth.

07:10.680 --> 07:12.420
Most folks have mixed spirit roots,

07:12.440 --> 07:14.010
two or three kinds combined.

07:14.200 --> 07:15.860
Only those with extraordinary talent

07:15.880 --> 07:16.690
possess a single spirit root.

07:17.270 --> 07:18.980
Anyone with a single spirit root

07:19.000 --> 07:20.100
is a rare cultivation prodigy.

07:21.120 --> 07:22.570
Single Wood Spirit Root.

07:26.270 --> 07:27.060
Let's go.

07:32.830 --> 07:33.740
Excuse me.

07:40.590 --> 07:41.450
Illusion talisman cheating!

07:41.830 --> 07:43.660
Kick him out and blacklist him for life.

09:19.710 --> 09:21.300
Top Metal Spirit Root.

09:29.350 --> 09:30.090
Metal Spirit Root.

09:31.040 --> 09:31.660
Pass.

09:35.870 --> 09:36.540
Wait a minute.

09:39.350 --> 09:41.140
Could it be another illusion talisman trick?

09:50.660 --> 09:52.690
Lei Yuan, it's really you.

09:57.160 --> 09:58.850
All those born with a Metal Spirit Root

09:59.230 --> 10:01.380
are destined for extraordinary immortal cultivation.

10:03.280 --> 10:04.850
Come study under me.

10:05.110 --> 10:06.690
I will pass down all my knowledge without reserve.

10:07.870 --> 10:08.490
No need.

10:19.040 --> 10:21.380
What's a Metal Spirit Root?

10:21.870 --> 10:23.330
I don't think he can be better than you.

10:23.660 --> 10:25.330
That old man must be senile.

10:27.660 --> 10:28.420
There is always someone stronger.

10:28.830 --> 10:31.090
We should treat gifted folks with courtesy

10:31.710 --> 10:32.490
and recruit them early.

10:36.510 --> 10:38.690
Your Metal Spirit Root sounds so powerful.

10:39.510 --> 10:40.210
Lend me some of it.

10:43.510 --> 10:46.020
Spirit roots cannot be lent to others.

10:46.510 --> 10:47.060
I…

11:03.990 --> 11:04.730
- Your turn. - I…

11:05.920 --> 11:06.690
She's calling you.

11:30.800 --> 11:31.730
No spirit root detected.

11:33.590 --> 11:35.020
Please check again.

11:35.040 --> 11:36.260
Check more closely.

11:36.630 --> 11:38.450
She truly has no spirit root at all.

11:40.990 --> 11:42.780
Please check more closely!

11:43.350 --> 11:45.690
Maybe my spirit root is hiding somewhere!

11:45.920 --> 11:46.610
Please.

11:46.990 --> 11:47.780
Check again.

11:49.510 --> 11:51.850
Xiaobangchui, hold your breath!

12:10.830 --> 12:12.450
W-What's that?

12:25.080 --> 12:28.540
Dual weak spirit roots with Wood primary, and Earth secondary.

12:31.800 --> 12:32.380
Pass.

12:35.830 --> 12:36.420
Thanks.

12:44.870 --> 12:47.330
Your meridians are sealed. No spirit roots can be detected.

12:49.870 --> 12:50.540
Passed.

12:52.200 --> 12:53.420
Clearly, it's a fox spirit's doing.

12:54.040 --> 12:55.210
Riyan lives inside her.

13:11.660 --> 13:12.420
Lei.

13:17.800 --> 13:18.420
What's up?

13:19.710 --> 13:21.060
Metal Spirit Roots are incredibly rare.

13:21.470 --> 13:24.060
May I see yours again?

13:25.230 --> 13:25.850
No time.

13:26.200 --> 13:26.850
Wait!

13:41.280 --> 13:43.450
We can team up

13:43.800 --> 13:44.660
for tomorrow's trial

13:44.920 --> 13:45.900
to get into the academy faster.

13:46.160 --> 13:47.300
I don't care about the academy.

13:49.510 --> 13:51.020
Then why sit the exam?

13:52.660 --> 13:53.900
Who exactly are you?

13:58.960 --> 14:00.490
Spirit or ghost,

14:00.590 --> 14:01.420
come out now!

14:02.160 --> 14:02.940
Or

14:05.200 --> 14:06.540
I'll shave all my hair off,

14:06.540 --> 14:07.450
so you'll have nowhere to hide.

14:08.160 --> 14:08.690
Wait.

14:11.750 --> 14:12.730
Are you really a girl?

14:12.960 --> 14:14.140
You'd sacrifice your own hair.

14:16.710 --> 14:18.490
You're that Qingqiu fox.

14:18.870 --> 14:19.680
[Riyan, Nine-Tailed Fox]

14:19.680 --> 14:21.730
I'm a Nine-Tailed Fox with a thousand years of cultivation.

14:22.110 --> 14:23.090
My name is Riyan.

14:23.710 --> 14:25.020
Ri as in sunlight,

14:25.230 --> 14:26.810
Yan as in blazing flame.

14:27.470 --> 14:29.690
Riyan.

14:31.040 --> 14:33.660
A thousand years of cultivation? Sounds powerful.

14:33.870 --> 14:34.900
Why'd you hide inside me?

14:35.350 --> 14:36.490
Only because your ma...

14:36.920 --> 14:38.900
I mean, you're such an unlucky fool.

14:38.920 --> 14:41.210
I'm willing to aid you. Show some gratitude!

14:41.400 --> 14:43.300
Come on! They were chasing you,

14:43.320 --> 14:44.330
and you hid on my head!

14:47.230 --> 14:47.730
Wait!

14:48.440 --> 14:51.020
You saw everything when I went

14:51.630 --> 14:52.690
to the latrine and bathed!

14:53.320 --> 14:56.180
My spirit body's injured, and all my senses shut down.

14:56.200 --> 14:56.810
Besides,

14:57.830 --> 14:58.810
what's there to see anyway?

15:04.110 --> 15:07.690
Your spirit body's hurt? Is it that bad?

15:07.750 --> 15:08.570
It's nothing much.

15:08.870 --> 15:10.940
Might take three to five years to heal fully.

15:10.960 --> 15:12.730
Three to five years? That's ages!

15:15.160 --> 15:16.330
Will you pay rent for hiding here?

15:17.350 --> 15:18.420
Ignorant girl!

15:19.110 --> 15:20.540
I've condescended

15:20.560 --> 15:22.060
to rest in your hair.

15:22.630 --> 15:23.780
This is an honor for you!

15:25.830 --> 15:27.210
Old spirit,

15:27.400 --> 15:29.020
you've grown shameless with age!

15:29.630 --> 15:30.940
So it's you.

15:31.160 --> 15:33.210
How many lovers have you ruined for centuries?

15:33.350 --> 15:34.210
What do you mean?

15:34.320 --> 15:36.730
[Little Matchmaker]
I match people up and build goodwill.

15:37.560 --> 15:38.940
You two know each other?

15:40.510 --> 15:41.450
When you live long enough,

15:41.680 --> 15:43.940
you're bound to meet shady folks.

15:44.710 --> 15:46.140
Right, stinky fox?

15:47.590 --> 15:48.570
He is here.

15:48.750 --> 15:49.380
Xiaobangchui,

15:50.630 --> 15:51.450
who are you talking to?

15:51.920 --> 15:52.940
No one at all!

15:56.160 --> 15:58.090
Come, I need to talk to you.

15:58.510 --> 15:59.210
Really?

16:05.160 --> 16:09.340
[Lugong Town]

16:26.240 --> 16:29.040
[Yange Hall]

16:31.200 --> 16:31.900
Thanks.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.330
Don't just stare.

16:43.080 --> 16:43.490
Here,

16:44.630 --> 16:45.260
have some meat.

16:56.200 --> 16:57.210
Trying to test me?

17:14.270 --> 17:17.250
Here. Drink some water to cut the grease.

17:22.440 --> 17:23.180
Drink with me.

17:30.920 --> 17:32.420
Still plotting against me.

17:39.230 --> 17:40.340
The truth-telling spell doesn't work.

17:56.230 --> 17:57.250
You poisoned the water too.

18:00.100 --> 18:01.970
Your head's spinning, right?

18:02.790 --> 18:04.140
You took my soul-bewitching powder,

18:04.160 --> 18:06.530
so your head is buzzing,

18:06.550 --> 18:07.660
and your tongue won't cooperate, huh?

18:08.710 --> 18:09.290
Yeah.

18:13.310 --> 18:15.690
Good. Tell me.

18:16.310 --> 18:17.380
Why are you getting close to me?

18:25.230 --> 18:27.290
Stop struggling. Tell the truth.

18:28.160 --> 18:29.180
After my money?

18:30.880 --> 18:31.940
Or my master?

18:33.160 --> 18:35.010
Who's your master?

18:36.400 --> 18:37.340
Not after my master.

18:38.160 --> 18:38.900
Then what?

18:39.990 --> 18:42.010
I... I need to survive

18:42.990 --> 18:43.820
to save my brother.

18:44.400 --> 18:46.770
Save your brother? None of my business.

18:53.070 --> 18:54.210
Won't talk, huh?

18:56.070 --> 18:57.140
Then meet your end.

18:58.510 --> 18:59.140
Excuse me,

18:59.340 --> 19:01.940
pay the bill before fighting, and take it outside.

19:02.340 --> 19:04.900
Otherwise, you can't afford

19:05.100 --> 19:07.100
to break all these teapots and cups.

19:07.200 --> 19:09.290
Thirty liang for this tea?

19:09.550 --> 19:11.050
You're robbing us!

19:13.880 --> 19:16.210
Can we... put it on credit?

19:16.640 --> 19:20.530
Sorry, no credit here.

19:21.360 --> 19:24.400
[Mr. Yan, Owner of Yange Hall]

19:32.840 --> 19:34.580
He's a natural opera performer!

19:37.790 --> 19:39.250
Truly outstanding.

19:42.750 --> 19:44.100
And he's got quite a temper.

19:46.880 --> 19:47.860
I like that.

19:51.200 --> 19:52.690
Mr. Yan. If you like him,

19:53.750 --> 19:55.140
I'll sell him to you. Interested?

19:57.840 --> 19:59.450
He masters both literary and martial arts,

19:59.710 --> 20:02.250
the finest talent in Lugong Town.

20:02.960 --> 20:03.730
The price is merely a meal,

20:04.340 --> 20:06.940
plus leaked trial questions. What a bargain!

20:24.640 --> 20:26.450
Why hasn't Xiuyuan come back yet?

20:28.880 --> 20:30.180
He has a single spirit root.

20:30.470 --> 20:32.580
Some mentor might have recruited him

20:32.710 --> 20:33.530
on the spot.

20:35.710 --> 20:37.380
You'd better worry about yourself.

20:37.790 --> 20:39.940
This trial is said to be tougher than the previous ones.

20:40.160 --> 20:41.580
By rough reckoning,

20:42.310 --> 20:45.010
less than ten percent will pass.

20:50.750 --> 20:52.210
Even I fell for such a low trick.

20:52.230 --> 20:53.860
Look, these exam questions are five years old.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.140
I told you they were unreliable.

21:03.340 --> 21:05.340
Yange Hall has stood in Lugong Town for centuries,

21:05.550 --> 21:07.490
yet nobody knows Mr. Yan's true background.

21:07.710 --> 21:09.420
How dare you buy exam questions from him?

21:11.920 --> 21:14.250
What a crafty old thing.

21:15.310 --> 21:18.450
I need to bring up a big shot

21:19.750 --> 21:21.250
to make him give out all the questions.

21:25.880 --> 21:28.420
Just some gifts, please accept them.

21:32.680 --> 21:34.290
These are predicted two-choice test questions sorted

21:34.710 --> 21:36.580
from past records.

21:37.070 --> 21:38.180
Your Highness, here you are.

21:42.790 --> 21:43.690
I'll open this for you.

21:52.200 --> 21:52.770
No...

21:56.510 --> 21:57.730
This is way too much!

21:58.100 --> 22:00.580
It covers astrology, divination

22:01.030 --> 22:02.940
and cultivation arts from every school.

22:04.030 --> 22:05.730
If you master all of this,

22:06.680 --> 22:07.690
I'm sure you'll pass the trials.

22:15.710 --> 22:17.010
This isn't just food.

22:17.270 --> 22:19.660
It's pure silver! Such extravagance.

22:20.680 --> 22:22.140
This suits me perfectly.

22:23.600 --> 22:24.420
Where's Lei Xiuyuan?

22:24.750 --> 22:25.770
Why isn't he with you?

22:26.510 --> 22:27.180
He...

22:28.030 --> 22:29.010
he is staying right where

22:29.030 --> 22:30.140
he ought to be.

22:40.440 --> 22:42.900
Flower Fairy, where are you?

22:45.200 --> 22:47.120
[Miaoqing]

22:49.230 --> 22:51.580
Flower Fairy? Demon Lord?

22:57.600 --> 22:59.730
Records of Immortals and Demons in the Sea of Illusory Love?

23:11.400 --> 23:12.380
Save me!

23:18.640 --> 23:19.340
Xiaobangchui!

23:27.270 --> 23:27.940
Help me!

23:31.790 --> 23:32.490
Get me out of here!

23:33.920 --> 23:35.450
This place is pretty nice.

23:35.680 --> 23:37.450
Stay here, or you'll bring me troubles.

23:37.880 --> 23:39.860
If you don't save me, I'll never let go.

23:40.510 --> 23:41.010
You!

23:44.230 --> 23:44.660
Let go of me!

23:45.400 --> 23:46.860
Your Highness.

23:46.880 --> 23:47.900
Help me!

23:48.550 --> 23:50.180
Please! Your Highness!

23:50.470 --> 23:51.100
Leave her be.

23:52.230 --> 23:52.770
Let go!

23:56.100 --> 23:56.620
Watch out!

24:14.200 --> 24:15.730
These assassins can't see a thing.

24:16.440 --> 24:17.660
Your Highness, run!

24:17.920 --> 24:18.970
They've come to kill you!

24:29.790 --> 24:30.420
Stop them!

24:41.550 --> 24:42.250
Let me go!

25:26.100 --> 25:28.530
Who dares stir up trouble here?

25:36.100 --> 25:36.690
Where are they?

25:45.790 --> 25:47.730
Thank you for saving us

25:47.750 --> 25:48.690
and chasing the killers away.

25:49.270 --> 25:49.900
You said

25:50.310 --> 25:52.140
they were targeting me.

25:54.200 --> 25:55.380
It doesn't matter who they targeted.

25:55.470 --> 25:57.140
All thanks to Your Highness,

25:57.160 --> 25:57.770
sheltered by heaven,

25:57.790 --> 25:59.100
we've all got a share of your fortune

25:59.100 --> 25:59.940
and made it out safe.

26:07.790 --> 26:10.450
Is Lei Xiuyuan the one you are looking for?

26:10.920 --> 26:11.420
Yes.

26:14.030 --> 26:15.690
He's got the Gaolu clan mark.

26:16.680 --> 26:20.580
Gaolu was destroyed long ago, and our whole clan was killed.

26:22.100 --> 26:23.620
To let me escape,

26:25.030 --> 26:26.860
my mom sent Lei Yuan, Mr. Lei's adopted kid,

26:27.640 --> 26:28.730
to pretend to be me

26:29.310 --> 26:32.180
and lead Wugou's and the Longming Sanctuary's killers away.

26:33.230 --> 26:34.450
He was only eleven,

26:36.960 --> 26:38.050
six months younger than me.

26:38.840 --> 26:40.010
Only Mr. Lu was with him.

26:41.880 --> 26:43.010
We all thought he died.

26:45.400 --> 26:46.210
Turns out

26:48.680 --> 26:49.530
he's alive.

27:04.340 --> 27:05.250
Get lost.

27:09.600 --> 27:10.580
I want to survive

27:11.100 --> 27:12.100
and find my brother.

27:13.200 --> 27:14.490
So pitiful.

27:15.510 --> 27:17.770
But none of my business.

27:32.160 --> 27:34.420
What? Save Lei Xiuyuan?

27:36.470 --> 27:38.860
Who said she'd obey every word

27:39.400 --> 27:40.140
I say?

27:40.990 --> 27:42.900
I don't mean to refuse,

27:43.840 --> 27:45.530
but this guy

27:46.840 --> 27:49.970
is unlucky, and I fear it will taint your luck.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.420
Nonsense!

27:52.920 --> 27:54.290
Tongzhou's luck

27:54.510 --> 27:56.010
won't be ruined by some wild guy.

27:56.440 --> 27:59.010
No. He's a walking bad luck magnet.

27:59.510 --> 28:00.100
Think about it.

28:00.310 --> 28:02.770
He alone brought death to his entire village,

28:03.070 --> 28:04.050
and even crossed the Longming Sanctuary.

28:04.160 --> 28:05.290
How ill-omened that is!

28:05.400 --> 28:06.530
No need to worry about that.

28:06.840 --> 28:07.940
Just get him out,

28:08.230 --> 28:10.180
and I'll let you join the trial with me.

28:13.600 --> 28:17.100
Do I have to go rescue him?

28:22.270 --> 28:24.290
Can't we just bribe Mr. Yan?

28:25.270 --> 28:26.770
You think I haven't thought of that?

28:27.100 --> 28:28.690
I tried bribing him ages ago,

28:29.200 --> 28:30.970
but he wouldn't accept

28:31.100 --> 28:31.970
whatever I offered.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.730
If even you can't sway him,

28:37.640 --> 28:39.730
I stand no chance at all.

28:40.750 --> 28:42.180
[Yue Law]
The Yue Law states clearly:

28:44.400 --> 28:47.900
Human traffickers get 300 cane blows, and two years of hard labor.

28:48.710 --> 28:50.010
Lugong Town is part of the Yue State, so…

28:50.990 --> 28:52.250
Since Your Highness wants him,

28:52.270 --> 28:54.100
I'll bring him back safe and sound.

29:03.230 --> 29:04.210
Hold your needle!

29:06.790 --> 29:07.820
Sir! Sir!

29:08.510 --> 29:09.050
Oh, no.

29:09.550 --> 29:11.860
Even if he is being stubborn,

29:11.880 --> 29:12.770
you can discipline him,

29:12.790 --> 29:13.820
but he doesn't deserve death.

29:14.440 --> 29:16.690
There is a Longming Sanctuary's toxic mark on his nape.

29:16.880 --> 29:18.660
I meant to cure him with the golden needle.

29:18.960 --> 29:19.820
But you burst in,

29:21.070 --> 29:22.210
and the needle struck the Fengchi acupoint.

29:24.990 --> 29:26.490
Now he's paralyzed in the face.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.860
He can't speak properly today.

29:32.200 --> 29:34.450
It's all a misunderstanding.

29:35.270 --> 29:35.970
Misunderstanding?

29:37.030 --> 29:38.180
You may use the front door,

29:38.440 --> 29:39.620
yet flew in through the window.

29:41.470 --> 29:42.660
To tell you the truth,

29:43.160 --> 29:45.420
I came here specially to visit you.

29:47.360 --> 29:49.730
Oh? Want to sell yourself to my hall too?

29:51.990 --> 29:54.730
About the unfinished opera from yesterday,

29:56.440 --> 29:57.690
I came to ask how it ends.

29:59.310 --> 30:02.100
You know Records of Immortals and Demons in the Sea of Illusory Love?

30:02.840 --> 30:04.660
Sure, I've read over twenty versions.

30:07.680 --> 30:08.860
Which version do you like best?

30:09.640 --> 30:10.860
The one marked Yan.

30:11.470 --> 30:14.730
It states the Flower Fairy giggles, turns around,

30:14.990 --> 30:15.940
lifts her skirt,

30:16.200 --> 30:18.490
and kicks the Demon Lord straight off the Immortal Execution Platform.

30:18.510 --> 30:20.450
So satisfying, utterly stirring!

30:25.160 --> 30:26.140
A kindred spirit!

30:28.120 --> 30:29.100
Let's talk inside.

30:29.470 --> 30:29.970
Alright.

30:33.070 --> 30:34.490
Make tea for our guest.

30:34.880 --> 30:36.290
Don't sit there like a log!

30:38.790 --> 30:39.730
Brew the finest tea.

30:41.840 --> 30:42.940
This way, please.

30:45.070 --> 30:46.770
Why not stay here and partner up with me?

30:47.440 --> 30:50.140
Let me tell you, with great stories in hand,

30:50.360 --> 30:51.900
we can dominate all realms.

30:51.990 --> 30:52.770
Sounds great!

30:53.550 --> 30:55.580
But I have to take the academy exam

30:55.990 --> 30:57.940
and find my family.

30:59.230 --> 30:59.730
You…

31:07.440 --> 31:09.530
What's wrong with you? So clumsy!

31:09.600 --> 31:10.620
Can't even serve tea properly.

31:12.880 --> 31:14.290
What? Want to beat me?

31:14.600 --> 31:15.050
Look.

31:16.160 --> 31:16.900
Mr. Yan,

31:17.440 --> 31:18.620
I run my business

31:18.710 --> 31:19.530
by one rule:

31:19.550 --> 31:21.010
top quality, fair prices, honest to both young and old.

31:21.470 --> 31:22.530
He is far from qualified.

31:23.400 --> 31:25.290
Look. I'll take him back to train properly

31:25.310 --> 31:26.380
and bring him back to you, alright?

31:27.710 --> 31:28.140
Let's go.

31:30.200 --> 31:32.250
Don't bother over such trivial matters.

31:32.550 --> 31:33.820
I'll train him myself.

31:34.310 --> 31:36.140
Think about it.

31:36.400 --> 31:38.580
You're swamped with work and still writing stories

31:38.600 --> 31:39.860
for us fans.

31:40.310 --> 31:42.210
How could I let you waste time on this?

31:42.790 --> 31:43.970
I'm taking him away now. Come on.

31:44.920 --> 31:45.530
Stop.

31:52.710 --> 31:55.730
Xiaobangchui, that's not fair play.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.770
I bought him with my money.

31:58.550 --> 32:00.340
You can't just take him away as you please.

32:03.400 --> 32:04.490
I'll pay you back the food cost.

32:04.960 --> 32:05.620
No need.

32:06.470 --> 32:09.250
Rare goods once sold, no refunds.

32:12.990 --> 32:14.490
I'm taking him away no matter what.

32:17.920 --> 32:18.380
Go!

32:24.640 --> 32:25.970
You can't take him away.

32:40.920 --> 32:42.580
You're not going anywhere today.

32:43.160 --> 32:43.660
You!

32:53.270 --> 32:53.860
Run!

33:03.270 --> 33:04.180
I'm returning him unharmed.

33:09.960 --> 33:11.730
The trial's starting. Get over there.

33:12.120 --> 33:14.050
You helped me?

33:15.880 --> 33:17.660
No problem. Let's take the trial together.

33:19.160 --> 33:22.050
That's great to have Your Highness with us.

33:26.920 --> 33:27.970
If you ever harm me again,

33:28.230 --> 33:30.380
I'll skin, dismember and sell you by weight.

33:33.990 --> 33:35.180
Your Highness has magic treasures,

33:35.840 --> 33:37.100
Lei Xiuyuan has spirit power,

33:37.400 --> 33:39.100
and I've got wits.

33:39.230 --> 33:40.860
We will be unbeatable.

33:43.030 --> 33:44.490
Let's go now.

33:46.600 --> 33:49.290
Only by slaying the host can I force the fox spirit out.

33:50.790 --> 33:51.490
Move.

33:58.030 --> 33:59.100
It's time.

33:59.990 --> 34:02.580
You have 24 hours from now.

34:02.840 --> 34:04.180
Make it out of this valley

34:05.200 --> 34:07.380
before noon tomorrow,

34:12.630 --> 34:15.700
and you'll pass the second trial.

34:32.550 --> 34:33.610
The trial begins.

34:53.880 --> 34:55.450
What are you doing here? Get away!

35:03.470 --> 35:04.010
Let's go.

35:23.880 --> 35:24.780
Your Highness!

35:26.700 --> 35:27.700
Your Highness!

35:28.590 --> 35:30.090
Anyone here?

35:35.630 --> 35:38.010
Tongzhou, are you still mad at me?

35:43.280 --> 35:44.090
Tongzhou,

35:44.550 --> 35:45.450
Xiaobangchui

35:45.470 --> 35:47.050
isn't on our side at all.

35:47.360 --> 35:49.300
I was afraid she'd slow us down.

35:49.880 --> 35:51.300
Still, you shouldn't be so reckless.

35:52.150 --> 35:53.170
If you do this again,

35:53.220 --> 35:54.220
I'll send you back.

35:54.760 --> 35:56.700
Alright. I won't do it next time.

35:56.960 --> 35:58.090
Don't send me away.

36:02.880 --> 36:04.610
Anyone here? Make a sound!

36:07.360 --> 36:09.970
Oh, no. I lost my powerful ally.

36:12.840 --> 36:13.610
It's freezing cold.

36:15.110 --> 36:15.970
Why is it so frigid?

36:15.990 --> 36:18.090
We must get out of here soon,

36:18.360 --> 36:18.860
or else…

36:34.670 --> 36:35.780
Bless me.

36:41.510 --> 36:42.300
This will work.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.700
The ancient Zhurong Stone.

38:03.990 --> 38:06.940
Xuanshanzi really splurged a fortune on this.

38:29.470 --> 38:30.780
Tongzhou, you're amazing!

38:33.700 --> 38:34.420
Let's go.

38:35.990 --> 38:38.970
Never thought someone so young

38:39.670 --> 38:41.300
could wield an ancient spirit treasure.

38:41.840 --> 38:44.650
Truly an extraordinary talent.

38:45.110 --> 38:47.380
He is using Xingzheng Hall's supreme treasure,

38:48.190 --> 38:50.700
so he's got a huge edge over other examinees.

38:51.590 --> 38:54.220
- Li, that's not right. - Stop arguing.

38:54.280 --> 38:55.220
Let's check the others.

38:55.320 --> 38:56.490
There may be someone stronger.

39:11.070 --> 39:11.970
No way,

39:12.840 --> 39:13.490
not this again.

39:34.760 --> 39:38.200
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

39:38.710 --> 39:41.120
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

39:41.600 --> 39:44.880
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

39:45.630 --> 39:46.490
It's you.

39:46.490 --> 39:47.160
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

39:48.150 --> 39:48.970
Where's His Highness?

39:50.820 --> 39:51.570
How should I know?

39:55.300 --> 39:57.090
Stay alive. I'm retreating.

40:06.980 --> 40:09.300
Bro... jump with me!

40:28.980 --> 40:32.490
All limbs intact, thank heavens I had a cushion.

40:37.360 --> 40:39.780
Can't attack openly, or the academy will find out.

40:46.300 --> 40:47.170
Lost your wits?

40:49.860 --> 40:51.860
It'd be easier if he really lost his wits.

40:55.630 --> 40:58.050
Say something. Are you alright?

40:58.470 --> 40:59.010
Speak to me.

41:01.630 --> 41:02.490
You're actually fine.

41:11.630 --> 41:12.170
Are you

41:14.340 --> 41:14.820
cold?

41:16.470 --> 41:18.130
Obviously, snow and ice are everywhere.

41:18.150 --> 41:19.090
Of course, I'm cold.

41:24.190 --> 41:25.970
What? Trying to trick me again?

41:26.630 --> 41:27.530
Don't move.

42:03.460 --> 42:04.650
Why's my whole body warming up?

42:10.340 --> 42:11.450
You're channeling your spirit power to me?

42:15.190 --> 42:17.170
No wonder I took a fancy to you, Metal Spirit Root.

42:17.420 --> 42:20.010
Putting others first, so kind and righteous.

42:20.670 --> 42:22.570
Those examinees are quite hopeful.

42:22.820 --> 42:23.740
Two more trials left.

42:30.190 --> 42:31.420
If I kill her now,

42:31.990 --> 42:33.610
the fox spirit may reveal itself to save her.

42:34.860 --> 42:37.740
Now's the chance to shatter her meridians.

42:42.160 --> 42:42.900
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.900 --> 42:44.760
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:56.800 --> 42:59.740
♪It's me, blinded by longing♪

42:59.900 --> 43:02.700
♪Every glance lands on you♪

43:02.860 --> 43:07.980
♪Fire and water clash, yet we cling inseparably♪

43:08.420 --> 43:11.260
♪Lotus broken, threads still bind us♪

43:11.580 --> 43:14.580
♪My heart calm till you stir storms and rain♪

43:15.220 --> 43:18.500
♪You are my destined rival♪

43:19.660 --> 43:24.620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

43:25.420 --> 43:30.740
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

43:31.300 --> 43:37.260
♪Bitterness brews sweet bliss, drained in one sip♪

43:37.700 --> 43:43.020
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

43:43.140 --> 43:48.740
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

43:48.820 --> 43:54.420
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred, they suit each other well♪

43:54.580 --> 44:00.620
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

44:01.060 --> 44:09.580
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪

44:18.820 --> 44:21.540
♪Sometimes I throw petty fits♪

44:21.820 --> 44:24.580
♪I blame all troubles on you♪

44:24.780 --> 44:29.900
♪Though distant on the surface, our souls resonate as one♪

44:30.340 --> 44:33.220
♪We wander far, parted to separate corners♪

44:33.500 --> 44:36.460
♪Yet my heart still leans toward you, my foe♪

44:37.140 --> 44:40.420
♪I sigh and laugh, defeated in this game of affection♪

44:41.660 --> 44:46.620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

44:47.340 --> 44:52.660
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

44:53.220 --> 44:59.180
♪Perhaps endless tangling is our silent bond♪

44:59.620 --> 45:04.940
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

45:05.060 --> 45:10.660
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

45:10.740 --> 45:16.340
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred, they suit each other well♪

45:16.500 --> 45:22.580
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

45:23.180 --> 45:32.380
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪
